        114.91,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0004",
      "text": " Alias Group Service Parameters (Alias_SP):",
      "bbox": [
        114.91,
        57.65,
        331.86,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0005",
      "text": " The Alias_SP defines the Service Parameters",
      "bbox": [
        331.86,
        57.65,
        540.12,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0006",
      "text": "to be used for all operations with this Alias Group.  The Service Parameters are passed as de-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        69.65,
        540.09,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0007",
      "text": "fined by the Common Service Parameters and the appropriate Class Service Parameters (see",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        81.65,
        539.99,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0008",
      "text": "6.6).",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        93.65,
        142.39,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0009",
      "text": "NOTE 4 – This field is used by the Fabric Controller to ensure that the Service Parameters to be used by the",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        117.86,
        539.89,
        127.9
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0010",
      "text": "Alias Group are not in conflict with the Fabric Service Parameters.",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        128.83,
        367.17,
        138.88
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0011",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        154.97,
        114.38,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0012",
      "text": "Nx_Port List Length (NP_List_Length):",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        154.97,
        306.52,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0013",
      "text": " The NP_List_Length specifies the number of entries",
      "bbox": [
        306.54,
        154.97,
        540.14,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0014",
      "text": "in the following NP_List.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        166.97,
        229.03,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0015",
      "text": "d)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        190.97,
        114.92,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0016",
      "text": " Nx_Port List (NP_List):",
      "bbox": [
        114.92,
        190.97,
        231.67,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0017",
      "text": " The NP_List contains one entry for each N_Port_ID to be included in",
      "bbox": [
        231.6,
        190.97,
        539.91,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0018",
      "text": "the Alias Group. The N_Port_ID shall not be an Alias_ID. The format of each NP_List entry is",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        202.97,
        540.03,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0019",
      "text": "as shown in ",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        214.97,
        177.89,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0020",
      "text": "table 79.",
      "bbox": [
        177.96,
        213.29,
        219.22,
        226.57
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0021",
      "text": "NOTE 5 – The Fabric Controller uses the NP_List to determine whether it  supports an Alias Group composed",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        313.21,
        539.95,
        323.26
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0022",
      "text": "of these Nx_Ports (e.g., if the Fabric does not support an Alias Group that spans Domains, and the NP_List",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        324.2,
        539.97,
        334.24
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0023",
      "text": "contains Nx_Ports in multiple Domains, the request may be rejected).  Alternatively, the Fabric may form an",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        335.18,
        540.03,
        345.22
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0024",
      "text": "Alias Group from the Nx_Ports within a single Domain. ",
      "bbox": [
        105.0,
        346.22,
        324.24,
        356.26
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0025",
      "text": "4.2.26.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        370.97,
        214.86,
        382.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0026",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        394.97,
        138.19,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0027",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies the rejection of the GAID Request.  An LS_RJT shall be returned if an",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        394.97,
        539.91,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0028",
      "text": "Alias_ID is not generated.  A reason code of \"Unable to perform command request\" shall be generat-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.97,
        540.08,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0029",
      "text": "ed, along with a reason code explanation given in table 147.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.97,
        361.44,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0030",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.97,
        142.05,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0031",
      "text": "The format of the Payload for the LS_ACC indicating that this request has been success-",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        442.97,
        539.99,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0032",
      "text": "fully completed is shown in table 80.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        255.97,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0033",
      "text": "The Alias Group Identifier field contains the Alias_ID that the Nx_Port shall recognize, in addition to",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        539.91,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p101_s0034",
      "text": "its native address identifier.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        217.1,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
